    "name": "My Slime Garden",
    "steam_appid": 3332460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras/d179200eda0abb0963ec89d5160c9ad2.avif?t=1772089652\" width=1560 height=987 /></span><br><strong>Welcome to a World of Squishy Adventure!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow, nurture, and unleash a team of lovable slimes with endless possibilities! In this enchanting survival journey, breed quirky slime combinations, face wild island challenges, and embrace the thrill of adventure with your gooey companions. Can you raise the perfect slime squad to brave the unpredictable elements and explore as far as the islands go?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras/72421aad47752146fd929ce1698514eb.avif?t=1772089652\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features: </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weekly Updates + Nightly Beta Builds!</strong><br>Weekly updates with new accessories and items to  increase the size of your collection and more! (Join the nightly beta option for semi-daily updates for new contents that will later be included in the weekly public builds!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Raise your slime in your own Slime Garden!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breed Unique Slimes</strong><br>Discover endless possibilities as you breed different slimes, combining traits from both parents to create new, one-of-a-kind slime companions with unique abilities and appearances.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras/942b6af93d0cb698a98958e6072499f1.avif?t=1772089652\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras_big/942b6af93d0cb698a98958e6072499f1.avif?t=1772089652 width=800 height=790 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feed and Train Slimes</strong> <br>Strengthen your slimes by feeding them, raising their stats, and unlocking new abilities. Proper care is essential for building a powerful team that can endure the challenges of survival.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dress up your Slime with over 100 Unique Accessories!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and buy new accessories to dress up your own slime!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras/1fc26420a0daed46d64ffcac78bb07c7.avif?t=1772089652\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras_big/1fc26420a0daed46d64ffcac78bb07c7.avif?t=1772089652 width=800 height=582 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelike Adventure</strong><br>Prepare your slime team for an ever-evolving island survival adventure, where every journey is unique. Face procedurally generated challenges, enemies, and rewards as you explore island after island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras/64989182d82e3afedc0637a05a64b378.avif?t=1772089652\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras_big/64989182d82e3afedc0637a05a64b378.avif?t=1772089652 width=1560 height=874 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fish to Earn Unique Rewards and Achievements!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras/8417fc9518d3009e06e747eb34909b8f.avif?t=1772089652\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras_big/8417fc9518d3009e06e747eb34909b8f.avif?t=1772089652 width=800 height=580 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Desktop Widget mode added so you can take them anywhere!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332460/extras/355bbafae71046a46e03c40dce8c5c04.avif?t=1772089652\" width=800 height=586 /></span></p></li></ul>",
